description: A delicious healthy side dish that can be enjoyed with any of your favourite meals.
name: Oven Roasted Zucchini Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Wash the zucchini thoroughly and cut both ends. Then cut in 4 quarters and then chop in medium sized cubes.
Place the zucchini cubes in a stainless bowl and season with olive oil, chilli flakes, salt, oregano and grated pecorino cheese. Toss well making sure all ingredients are well combined.
Using a tray with baking paper, spread the cubed zucchini evenly over the tray.
Bake for 20 minutes or until golden brown.
Remove from tray and transfer to plate. Enjoy as a side dish with your favourite meal.
